<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>{% block title %}TrekSwap{% endblock %}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        {% block body %}{% endblock %}
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>Cet email a été envoyé automatiquement, merci de ne pas y répondre.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 